sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant Frontend as Frontend React
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Client->>Frontend: Saisit email + mot de passe
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/login
    Gateway->>Auth: Proxy requête
    Auth->>DB: SELECT user WHERE email
    DB-->>Auth: Utilisateur trouvé
    Auth->>Auth: Vérifie le hash (bcrypt.compare)
    alt Mot de passe correct
        Auth->>Auth: Génère Access Token (15min)
        Auth->>Auth: Génère Refresh Token (7j)
        Auth->>DB: Sauvegarde Refresh Token
        Auth-->>Gateway: {accessToken, refreshToken, user}
        Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK
        Frontend->>Frontend: Stocke tokens (localStorage)
        Frontend-->>Client: Redirection dashboard
    else Mot de passe incorrect
        Auth-->>Gateway: 401 Identifiants invalides
        Gateway-->>Frontend: Erreur
        Frontend-->>Client: Affiche message d'erreur
    end
